headline: Marriott hits 100-hotel milestone in Saudi Arabia
summary: The new hotel is scheduled to open in 2030. It will form part of the Masar destination, an urban development overseen by Umm Al Qura for Development and Construction.

headline: Kasa CEO on Sonder’s fatal flaw, property takeover after collapse
summary: Apart-hotel company Kasa is slated to add several Sonder properties following its abrupt wind-down, which CEO Roman Pedan says resulted, in part, from Sonder’s master-lease operating approach.
